-- Open issue 7: The predicate ac_reach_2 uses Profile_UI in op.channel similarly.
-- Open issue 8: The predicate tc_PROF_01_holds uses Registration_API in op.channel.kind but op.channel.kind is a set of IfaceKind, not a set of Interface; this is a type mismatch.
-- Open issue 9: The predicate tc_PROF_02_holds uses Profile_UI in op.channel.kind similarly.
